      "title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
      "items": [
        {
          "question": "How does the Shopify integration work?",
          "answer": "You establish a secure connection via OAuth. You grant access to your store's data, and we automatically sync your orders. Setup takes 2 minutes."
        },
        {
          "question": "Is my data secure?",
          "answer": "Yes. Your Shopify access tokens are encrypted with AES-256. Supabase Row Level Security ensures each store only accesses its own data."
        },
        {
          "question": "Which shipping companies are supported?",
          "answer": "In Turkey: Yurtiçi Kargo, Aras Kargo, and MNG Kargo. Globally, via EasyPost: UPS, FedEx, and DHL."
        },
        {
          "question": "What does the free trial include?",
          "answer": "You get all Growth plan features for 14 days. Limited to 20 returns. No credit card required, cancel anytime."
        },
        {
          "question": "Can I customize the customer portal?",
          "answer": "Yes. Logo, colors, welcome message, and return reasons are fully customizable. Enterprise plan includes custom domain support."
        },
        {
          "question": "Can I use it with my team?",
          "answer": "Yes. Starter includes 1, Growth includes 5, and Enterprise includes unlimited team members."
        }
      ]
